      <item>
        <title>Hammer - weird layout</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[chrisp]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Try going to Tools -&gt; Options -&gt; General (tab) -&gt; Untick ‘Use Independent Window Config’</p>
<p>Edit: You would need to reload any open map.</p>
          <p><a href="https://leakfree.org/t/hammer-weird-layout/3486/3">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
